        </div>

        <div class="col-4">
            <P>Warrior 2 is an external hip opener and opens up the inner thighs and groin. It's a good starting point for many side postures including triangle, extended angle and half moon balance.

                How to do it: Stand with your feet one leg’s-length apart.

            </P>

